<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 02 at 4:25AM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...WIDESPREAD LIGHT SNOW CONTINUES THIS MORNING...
Widespread light snow will continue into the mid to late morning
hours, tapering off between 8 AM to 10 AM. Fluctuations in
snowfall intensity and reductions in visibility is expected with
the ongoing activity. Drivers are urged to exercise caution and
take it slow this morning.
&amp;&amp;
PRECAUTIONARY/PREPAREDNESS ACTIONS...
* Prepare, plan and stay informed. Visit http://go.usa.gov/c7kkP</description>
